  <li>I'm asking why you left the door unlocked.</li>
</ul>

<blockquote class="highlight-right">
  <p>You can use ã‚ãªãŸ as a formality to sound rational and professional when you communicate negative emotions, such as anger, hatred, hostility, or a sense of rivalry.</p>
